                <!-- Scope of Practice Section -->
                <section id="scope" class="lesson-section">
                    <div class="section-header">
                        <h2><i class="fas fa-balance-scale"></i> Scope of Practice vs. Standards of Care</h2>
                        <p>Understand the legal and professional boundaries for medical assistants.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="card">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-gavel"></i> Key Definitions</h3>
                        
                        <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 20px; margin-top: 20px;">
                            <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 300px; background: #f0f7ff; padding: 20px; border-radius: var(--radius);">
                                <h4 style="color: var(--primary-purple);">Scope of Practice</h4>
                                <p><strong>Definition:</strong> The procedures, actions, and processes that a healthcare practitioner is permitted to undertake according to their professional license or certification.</p>
                                <ul style="margin-top: 10px; padding-left: 20px;">
                                    <li>Defined by state laws</li>
                                    <li>Varies by state</li>
                                    <li>Based on education & training</li>
                                    <li>Legal boundary for practice</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 300px; background: #fff0f7; padding: 20px; border-radius: var(--radius);">
                                <h4 style="color: var(--accent-blue);">Standards of Care</h4>
                                <p><strong>Definition:</strong> The degree of care and skill that the average qualified healthcare professional would provide in similar circumstances.</p>
                                <ul style="margin-top: 10px; padding-left: 20px;">
                                    <li>Defined by professional organizations</li>
                                    <li>Consistent across states</li>
                                    <li>Based on best practices</li>
                                    <li>Quality benchmark for practice</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="card">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i> Scope of Practice Scenarios</h3>
                        <p>Determine whether each scenario is within a medical assistant's scope of practice:</p>
                        
